Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤了吗？\NAre you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我很好\NNo, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jess  他们杀了Tara\NJess, they-- they killed Tara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  我知道\NYeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我难以相信\NI can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你在哪儿？\NWait, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,额\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在Bellefleur这里\NI'm at the Bellefleurs'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我为他们提供保护\NI offered them my protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我得保护Adilyn\NI'm going to protect Adilyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你进食了吗？\NHave you fed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  我…我不饿\NIt's okay, I'm-- I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jess 你得进食\NJess, you have to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我  等会儿见  好吗？\NI-- I'll see you later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  好\NYeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是只狗\NYou're a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了\NI just saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚是狗  你变回来的\NYou were a dog, you turned back into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那他妈是咋回事儿？\NWhat the fuck was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,听着Vince  Norris市长同意的时候\NLook, Vince, when Mayor Norris passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你我可是经过一场激烈论辩的\Nyou and me fought a hard campaign against each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不怪你吃不到葡萄说葡萄酸\Nso I don't blame you for sour grapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但你要告诉这些人我是只狗？\Nbut you tell these people their mayor's a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  这只会让他们觉得你是疯了\NSee, all that's gonna do is make you look crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别说我看到的啥都不是\NDon't tell me I didn't see what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈就是只狗\NYou were a motherfucking dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我了个去  好好  你看到的没错\NGod damn it, fine. All right, you saw what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看看四周  Vince\NTake a look around this place, Vince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿的人几乎坚持不下去了\NFolks here are barely holding on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再扔一个炸弹  人们会更恐慌\NWe throw them another curveball, people are gonna panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那你他妈到底是啥？\NWhat the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你一切\NI'll tell you everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Vince  但我们得先度过此关\NVince, but not until we get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为这个你我都爱的小镇\NFor the sake of the town we both love,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我请求你  拜托了\NI am begging you, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,能先你我两人保密吗？\Ncan we keep this between us just for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托？\NPlease?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  听着各位\NHey, listen up, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿不安全\NIt's not safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那些病毒吸血鬼们随时可能回来\NThose Hep-V vamps could be back any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得让吸血鬼带领他们指定的人类\NWe need every vampire to take their assigned human
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,安全的回到他们的家\Nback to the safety of their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  如果每个反抗病毒吸血鬼的人类\NAnd there, if every Hep-V negative human
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为他们的吸血鬼提供给养\Nwould kindly feed their vampire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,换取他们的保护\Nin exchange for their protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就有机会挺到明早\Nwe got a better chance of making it through till the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,明早\NNow, tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在Daniel牧师教堂见\Nwe're gonna meet up at Reverend Daniels' church
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,试着找出方法帮助人们\Nto try and figure out how to help those folks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,避免伤害  请相互告知\Nwho've been hit, so please spread the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人类呢？\NYou have a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,过来  我带你回家\NCome on. I'm gonna get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回家  市长先生\NLet's get you home, Mr. Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不  谢了老兄  我没事\NNo, thanks, man, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一人一鬼  这是你说的\NEvery vampire a human. This was your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,人们得看到你也是这样\NPeople need to see you sticking to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  我是Sookie\NHey, this is Sookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在不在  请留言\NI'm not in right now. Please leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你去哪儿了？我在找你\NHey, where'd you go? I'm looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该回去了\NWe should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,332)}来看“猎鹿人”了\NWe watch "Deer Hunter."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&Hd22c01&\fn楷体\fs20\4c&H000000&\pos(376,50)}猎鹿人：电影  这里指打枪游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么？  - 滚你丫\N- What is your name? - Go fuck yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,滚你丫小姐\NThe lady "Go Fuck Yourself"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,挑战者优先\NChallenger go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我幸存了27次\NI've survived 27 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,27\N27.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,28次\N28.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真主阿拉爱我呢\NAllah loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你的上帝爱你吗？\NDoes your god love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我的上帝恨死我了\NNope, my god fuckin' hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,世界正在走向灭亡\NThe world is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要和你的上帝和平共处\NYou need to make peace with your god.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱的人都走了  我接触的人都死了\NEveryone I love leaves, everything I touch dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果我不和上帝说你的信仰  请原谅我\Nso forgive me if I don't share your faith in my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他能拯救你  - 恩  告诉你\N- He can save you. - Yeah, tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你我的上帝什么\NYour god and my god can go to a motel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕在他们在旅馆瞎搞\Nand have a circle jerk for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只是在地狱和恶魔交易\NI'll be in Hell having a three-way with the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,辞藻空洞\NYour words are hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看到你眼中的爱与痛\NI can see the love and pain in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这种感觉…\NBecause this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让你此时此刻接近上帝  不是吗\Nright now makes you closer to God, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,让你知道你还活着？\NMakes you know you're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你死定了\NYou're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不会\NNo, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我还活着\NI'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我的制造者在哪儿？\NSo where the fuck's my maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你得去见这个人\NThis is who you have to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉你朋友\NI'm sorry about your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就算窗户开着\NYou can't come in here, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你也不能进来  是吗？  - 对\N- Even though the window's open? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你的邀请我无法进入\NI can't come in without an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这规定真奇怪\NThat's kind of a weird rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,恩\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到了你之前对我爸爸说的\NI heard what you said to my dad before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说你不想伤害我\NAbout not wanting to hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\NI meant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我会做关于那晚的噩梦\NI have nightmares about that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\NMe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我的血  是吗？\NIt's 'cause of my blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对吸血鬼来说我闻起来不同？\NI smell different to vampires?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,恩\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对你我还是很好闻吗？\NDo I still smell good to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你会杀了我吗？\NAre you gonna kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那你要是控制不住呢？\NWell, what if you can't help it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该恨你的\NI should hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没有\NBut I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你男友吗？\NWas that your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,电话里  是你男友吗？\NOn the phone, was that your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  恩  是\NOh, yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他长什么样子？\NWell, what's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他…他很可爱\NHe's-- he's so loving
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有几分绅士\Nand kind and gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还很性感\Nand he's hot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  他  真的很性感\NYeah, he's, like, sexy as heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你有男友吗？\NDo you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么个男孩  我也说不准\NThere's this one boy, but I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫什么？\NWhat's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wade\NWade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Holly的孩子？\NHolly's boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你迷恋Holly的儿子？\NYou have a crush on Holly's boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  不算迷恋  - 是  你就是\N- No, not a crush exactly. - Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她是谁？\NWhat is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的\NShe's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你独自回家了\NYou walked home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,经过今晚发生的\NAfter what happened tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那些在树林里寻觅我们的\Nit ain't a question of whether these Hep-V vamps
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,病毒吸血鬼们都不是事儿了\Nare out there in the woods looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道他们就在外边Sookie\NWe know they're out there, Sookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么还这样做？\NWhy would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我读了你的思想  - 什么？\N- I read your thoughts. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  我知道我不应该\NI'm sorry, I know I'm not supposed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我今晚没有缓冲\Nbut I got no buffer tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也不想...它们就这么跑脑子里... - Sookie\N- And I can't-- they just keep coming in... - Sookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得其他人都有可能这样想\N...and I expect it from everybody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是你不会的 - 什么？\N- but not from you. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该爱我  并且支持我\NYou're supposed to love me and support me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是即使是你也因为这个在怪我\Nand even you are blaming me for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为了这个小镇所发生的事情责怪我\Nblaming me for what's happened to this town
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,把Arlene的失踪也怪到我头上\Nand blaming me for Arlene being missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我没有\NNo, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我能听到你的想法\NI read your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sookie  这不公平 - 我知道\N- Sookie, it ain't fair. - I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样带有色眼镜看我\NIt ain't fair to judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,并且把我拒之门外\Nand push me away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为我内心的一些想法\N'cause of something I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的想法我都知道\NI know that, too.
