Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.61,0:42:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记我是这个教区的警探\Nof this parish for just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.52,0:43:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,用枪指着人真可谓是个大交易\NFiring a weapon at another human being is a big fucking deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.32,0:43:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦做了  扣动扳机\NWhen you do it, when you pull that trigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.06,0:43:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你就再也没有回头路了\Nyou are crossing a line you can never come back from.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.83,0:43:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,放下它\NPull it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.30,0:43:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人生就不一样了\NYour life's never gonna be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.70,0:43:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定这是你想要的\NYou be sure this is what you wanna do
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.70,0:43:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我会扣下我的扳机  Luo\N'cause I will pull my fucking trigger, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.31,0:43:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我会打一枪  然后再补一枪\NI've done it before and I'll do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.07,0:43:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  我真会的\NSo help me, God, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.65,0:43:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以快离开这儿\NGet the hell outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.46,0:43:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  回家  这儿不安全\NGo on, go home. It's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.36,0:43:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信你刚的选择\NI can't believe you're just gonna stand by
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.56,0:43:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你让这吸血鬼血洗小镇\Nand let these H-vamps kill our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.66,0:43:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪边也不选\NAin't nobody standin' by.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.23,0:43:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,事态还会继续的\NIt's to be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.34,0:43:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不  孩子  这儿的该结束了\NNo, son, this shit's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.61,0:43:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,走！\NGet!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.91,0:43:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  伙计  这家伙估计喝多了\NCome on. Man, he's drunk anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.90,0:44:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊！\NJesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.34,0:44:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们永远出不去了\NWe ain't never gonna make it outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.11,0:44:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\NNot ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.08,0:44:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,良辰镇就一个五人警队\NBon Temps got a police force of five people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.48,0:44:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我是其中之一\Nand I'm one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.02,0:44:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是真的  Andy会找到我们的\NThat is not true. Andy's gonna find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.78,0:44:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在什里夫波特！\NWe are in Shreveport!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.78,0:44:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&Hd22c01&\fn楷体\fs20\4c&H000000&\pos(368,50)}什里夫波特：美国路易斯安那州西北部城市
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.05,0:44:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼酒吧的地下室！\NIn the basement of some fangbanger bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.26,0:44:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能及时找到我们吗？\NHow they gonna find us in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.06,0:44:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.56,0:44:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能死这儿  我还有孩子啊\NI can't die down here. I've got kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.93,0:44:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  保持清醒  Arlene\NNo, no, no, no. You've gotta keep your head up, Arlene.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.40,0:44:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,听到没？\NYou hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.28,0:44:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不许在我面前胡思乱想\NI can't have you losing it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.27,0:44:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  嘿  会没事的\NHey, hey, hey, it's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.37,0:44:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们会没事的  - 我感觉不到她了\N- We're gonna be okay. - I can't feel her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.91,0:45:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为她…\NI don't think she's--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.95,0:45:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她会没事的  她很好\NShe's gonna be okay. She's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.24,0:45:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊\NOh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.28,0:45:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,低下头  保持安静\NKeep your head down and be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.68,0:45:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会死的\NWe're all gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.88,0:45:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊  哦  天啊\NOh, God. Oh, God. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.32,0:45:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  上帝  求你了\NOh, please, God. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.92,0:45:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊  不要  求你  求求你了\NOh, God, please don't. Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.06,0:45:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哦不  哦  不\NOh, no. Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.00,0:45:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.40,0:45:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,求你  不要  不要\NPlease, please, don't. Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.85,0:45:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,求你  别杀我\Nplease, please, don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.73,0:45:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,求你  求你  求求你\NPlease, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.67,0:45:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,求你  求你  不要  不要杀我\NOh, please, please don't. Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.91,0:45:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.05,0:45:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不  不\NOh, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.45,0:45:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想都别想\NNo fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.32,0:45:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.12,0:45:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必这样的\NYou don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.12,0:46:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  刚的事情  我想说谢谢\NLook, I wanna say thank you for what you did back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.99,0:46:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚之所以救你是需要你帮我\NI saved your miserable hide because I need your help
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.29,0:46:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,救回Holly和Arlene\Nto get Holly and Arlene back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.16,0:46:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这不代表我们友好\NBut we are not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.06,0:46:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也绝不会友好\NWe will never be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.20,0:46:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这世界上也没有什么东西可以弥补\NThere ain't nothing in this world can make right
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.06,0:46:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我及我家人的所作所为\Nwhat you done to me and my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.17,0:46:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以省省你的谢谢\NSo save your thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.66,0:47:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  爸爸\NBye, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.13,0:47:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明来了  你该走了\NDawn's coming. You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.27,0:47:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿为她而死吗？\NYou're willing to die for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.77,0:47:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会离开的\NI am not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.56,0:48:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有个阁楼！\NWe have an attic!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.16,0:48:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.46,0:48:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你在外边会死的！\NYou're gonna die out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.43,0:48:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,呆在屋里  别邀请我\NYou stay inside. Do not invite me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.00,0:48:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你\NI trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.43,0:48:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应该相信\NYou shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.47,0:48:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica  我邀请你进来\NJessica, I invite you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.74,0:48:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我擦\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.54,0:48:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我邀请你进来！\NI invite you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.51,0:48:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不不\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.65,0:48:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,让我进来  你个贱婊子！\NLet me in, you fucking bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.19,0:48:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让我进去！\NLet me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.49,0:48:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  小妞\NCome on, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.13,0:48:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的啊\NI've gotta make her mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.73,0:48:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我进去！\NLet me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.30,0:48:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你个婊子！\NYou bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.07,0:48:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不\NNo! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.04,0:48:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.41,0:48:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  兄弟姐妹们  昨晚\NYes, brothers and sisters, it has been night
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.58,0:49:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,长夜难熬\Na long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.85,0:49:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但我今晨醒来  向上帝祷告\NBut when I got up today, I prayed to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.12,0:49:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,请求他的指引\NI asked Him for guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.96,0:49:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我倾心聆听\NI strained to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.29,0:49:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我\NAnd He told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.30,0:49:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“清晨已至”\N"Morning is coming."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.23,0:49:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  他说的对  清晨已至\NYes, He did. Morning is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.44,0:49:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们一起说  阿门  - 阿门\N- Let the church say, "Amen." - All: Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.44,0:49:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们需要相信我  上帝之子\NYou have to believe me, children of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.74,0:49:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还和上帝同在\Nthat when you stay with the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.78,0:49:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,亲附他\Nif you cling to Him,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.64,0:49:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还坚守他\Nif you abide in Him,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.25,0:49:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  那会让你抓住清晨一瞥\Nwell, then, He'll let you catch a glimpse of the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.72,0:49:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很难再说什么\NIt's hard to know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.82,0:49:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的社区遭遇袭击\NOur community has been raided.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.09,0:49:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,别把手放我肩上  Sookie Stackhouse\NDon't you put your hand on me, Sookie Stackhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.50,0:49:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我宝贝的死都是你的错\NIt's your fault my baby's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.00,0:49:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她总是会追随你\NShe always went running to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.83,0:49:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你却让她倒下了\NAnd you led her down the path to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.67,0:49:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这上帝之所不欢迎你\NYou are not welcome in this house of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.01,0:50:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,无耻荡妇\NFucking slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.94,0:50:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,麻痹吸血鬼淫妇\NVampire-fucking bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.26,0:50:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不跑向你那鬼情人？\NWhy don't you run back to your vampire lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.35,0:50:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 操你丫的  荡妇  - 她不觉得无耻吗？\N- I wanna fuck you, vampire fucker. - Has she no shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.48,0:50:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 滚出去  傻蛋  - 真希望她离开\N- Get out, you stupid cunt. - I wish she would leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.22,0:50:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 捅你妹啊  - 草泥马该死的\N- Vampires flock to you like geese. - I'm wanna fuckin' kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.79,0:50:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还得待多久啊？ - 伤透了心\N- How long can I stay off? - Stab you through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.89,0:50:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你快离开小镇吧  你不属于这儿\NRun you out of town. You don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.53,0:50:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我能听到你们说的\NI can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.03,0:50:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们每个人说的我都能听到\NI can hear each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.33,0:50:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,至少Lettie Mae会体面的说\NAt least Lettie Mae's got the decency
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.93,0:50:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她对我的看法\Nto say what she thinks to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.51,0:50:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生都居住在良辰镇\NI've lived in Bon Temps my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.78,0:50:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱这小镇\NAnd I love this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.98,0:50:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我这一生也都在聆听你们\Nand I've known all of you my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.55,0:50:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你们大部分都恨我\NAnd even though most of you hate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.12,0:50:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可我就是爱你们每个人\NI love just about everybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.19,0:50:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们大部分人怎么看我\NAnd I know what most of you think of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.52,0:50:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一些人把发生的事归罪于我\Nthat some of you blame me for what's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.59,0:50:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这不错\NAnd you're not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.60,0:50:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是原因之一\NI played a part,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.71,0:50:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但事情回不到从前\Nbut we can't go back to the way things were
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.87,0:51:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也无法拯救那些失去的人\Nand I can't save those who have been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.34,0:51:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们的一些朋友  爱人\NBut some of our friends and loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.54,0:51:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,正在为活着的人奋战\Nare fighting for their lives right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.01,0:51:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不管好坏\Nand for better or for worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.61,0:51:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这小镇没人比我更了解吸血鬼\Nnobody in this town knows vampires better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.35,0:51:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想帮忙\NI wanna help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.42,0:51:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我帮忙\NPlease let me help.
